## What happened

To be honest, I'm not sure when exactly this error happened. I saw a red banner showing the error just after I clicked to terminate a running Profile session on a connected mobile phone (via pressing the Stop button in Android Studio). But the banner might have been there before.

## Version information

Android Studio `Bumblebee | 2021.1.1` • Flutter plugin `io.flutter 63.2.2` • Dart plugin `211.7798`

Flutter 2.10.0 • channel stable • https://github.com/flutter/flutter.git
Framework • revision 5f105a6ca7 (10 days ago) • 2022-02-01 14:15:42 -0800
Engine • revision 776efd2034
Tools • Dart 2.16.0 • DevTools 2.9.2
